        <updateDate>2021-06-08T20:01:30Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Carbon Cost Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to coordinate with the National Academy of Sciences to study alternatives for a nonpartisan congressional office or agency to make science-based projections of the effect of federal legislation on global greenhouse gas emissions.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
